OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will begin dry and
OL,6,Fsunny with patchy frost. Cloud will
OL,7,Fspread east during the morning and
OL,8,Fshowers will build during the
OL,9,Fafternoon, some of these may be heavy
OL,10,Fwith hail and thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe evening will be cloudy
OL,13,Fwith showers. These showers will die
OL,14,Ffrom late evening as clear spells
OL,15,Fspread west, leading to a frosty end
OL,16,Fto the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
