OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA frosty, dry and sunny start
OL,6,Fto the day will be followed by
OL,7,Fbuilding cloud during the morning and
OL,8,Fpatchy rain spreading north towards
OL,9,Fthe evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBands
OL,12,Fof rain push northeast with showers,
OL,13,Fsome heavy and thundery, following
OL,14,FWednesday. These showers continue in
OL,15,Fthe south Thursday. A further rain
OL,16,Fband pushes northeast Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
